snippet.textDisplay:
Wow! I'm so late here. But, so much to appreciate here. The one thing I love about coke studio is that it always brings a bunch of people who are truly passionate and talented in music. The performance becomes all the more loveable when we can see the love, passion and the artists truly enjoying themselves in it & I can see it here. It's not about just vocals, it's about each and everyone that is involved that creates the magic. I'm in love with the clean vocals of both the singers, harmony, the amazing blend of genres and music arrangement, the lightings and videography and stage setting. Kudos to the entire team❤...
PS: The hand jewellery of female singer caught my eyes though...
